Test Case 3 – Register New User and Logout

Test Objective:
Verify that a new user can register successfully and log out.

Test Steps:

    Launch the website https://automationexercise.com/

    Click on Signup / Login from the menu.

    In the New User Signup section, enter a name and a unique email.

    ClSiick gnup.

    Fill out the required registration details (password, DOB, address, etc.).

    Click Create Account.

    Verify that a success message “Account Created!” appears.

    Click Continue and verify user is logged in.

    Click Logout from the menu.

    Verify that user is redirected to login page.

Expected Result:
New user should be registered successfully, automatically logged in, and able to log out.